data.description: This West Bloomfield home offers a luxurious living experience with an generously sized updated eat in kitchen with granite countertops, creating an elegant and modern feel.  The newer roof & electric vehicle charger is a bonus.  You will fall in love with the spacious master suite featuring a natural fireplace, nice large bathroom & plenty of closet space. The 2nd bedroom has an substantial amt of space with access to a full bath.  The family room boasts a cozy natural fireplace too.  When you step into the living room there's three door walls to access the deck and a nice dining area with abundant windows to allow natural light, enhancing the overall ambiance of the home.  This home is located 2 doors down from a walking trail & right in the heart of highways, shopping & restaurants....
